msg: Previous commit broke the XmlSchema build on Sun derived 1.5 vms (Solaris and OS X at least) as the xalan classes have been repackaged. This change reverts the default behaviour. To run the build pointing to the classes packaged in an IBM JVM, run the build with a -DisIBM=true For info about the sun renaming see http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.5.0/docs/guide/xml/jaxp/JAXP-Compatibility_150.html#packageNames
I'll confirm this works on an IBM vm momentarity
